abstract: Pakistani police report the wounding of Chief Justice Ghulam Mustafa Mughal by an unidentified gunman in the Pakistani-controlled part of Kashmir.
snippet: An unidentified gunman wounded the chief justice of the high court in the Pakistani-controlled part of the disputed Kashmir region on Tuesday, the police said.
lead_paragraph: An unidentified gunman wounded the chief justice of the high court in the Pakistani-controlled part of the disputed Kashmir region on Tuesday, the police said.

headline.seo: Judge Wounded by Gunman in Pakistan-Controlled Kashmir
